Available Tools: send_sms | send_bulk_sms | get_sms_status | get_sms_history
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "to": "string", "message": "string", "from": "string" }
Response Schema: { "message_id": "string", "to": "string", "status": "string", "cost": number, "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: Send a welcome message to a new subscriber in Madrid.
Call: { "func_call": "send_sms", "to": "+34612345678", "message": "Welcome to FitLife! Your journey starts now. Reply STOP to opt out.", "from": "FitLifeES" }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_es_7738291", "to": "+34612345678", "status": "sent", "cost": 0.039, "timestamp": "2023-10-27T15:01:12Z" }

